reviews.customers_say: Customers find the dress fits well, with one mentioning it goes past the knees, and appreciate its flattering design that hugs the body in all the right places.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gorgeous and comfortable
items.body: I bought this after seeing one of the influencers and they got this right. This is such a comfortable and beautiful color combo. I got the Medium. I am 5'0 and 150 lbs. It was very flattering. Yes the dress top is weird stitching for some, but I am ok with it. Overall it is great. I bought 3 colors and they were all worth it. Very warm and thick. I got compliments all day. Read more
items.author: Essie A.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful winter wear
items.body: OMG this sweater dress was amazing! It is a perfect weight and not sheer at all for a winter date and it fit like a glove. The shrug made the perfect accent to the set just in case it gets a little chilly. I would buy again it in every color. I Added note I haven’t washed it yet but when I do I’ll add to the comment about how it does. Read more
items.author: Lize

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable and stretchy
items.body: The media could not be loaded. Omg!! So comfy and stunning! I got an xL which is what I normally wear and it was just right. The cardigan was a great fit and everything just flowed. It material wasn’t too thick this can literally be a winter and/or fall fit!! I will be getting more colors! Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Hot, modest dress
items.body: The dress portion fit phenomenal; I didn’t keep it because it was a little too modest for my taste; the shawl thing however was an awkward fit, hence 4 stars; if you wear the dress alone it’s super cute and recommend Read more
items.author: KRamos147

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars It’s comfortable and easy going
items.body: This is so comfy , the size is perfect , love the quality , easy to put on and go , the attention u get when wearing this dress … u gots to try for ur self… Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits and Looks great
items.body: This dress is incredible. Excellent fit, slimming and so trendy. I will get more colors for sure. Loved it. Read more
items.author: Natasha Danielle

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just buy it
items.body: Loved loved loved this dress. It’s the perfect thickness. Not too much to be uncomfortable but enough I couldn’t feel the cool evening air going through. Cover up fit well too. I read some reviews that said it fit small and I disagree. I have big arms and I was comfortable. The dress is well made and not one of these cheap looking dresses that fall apart after one wash. I’m on a weight loss journey and between a size L and XL and I got the L and I was very happy with it. Im 5’6” 205lbs for reference. It does snag a little easier than I’d like but still worth it. The only thing I did not like is that it already had the smell of perfume on it so I think it may have been worn. I washed it immediately and hung to dry. Read more
items.author: Stephanie

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Repeated issues
items.body: During the Black Fridays sale I ordered one and there was a weird line across the butt. I returned and ordered a new one and this one right out of the bag has a snag . Now the sale is over and I’m sad . Read more
items.author: Moriah

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Maxi Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Maxi Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Brown, Blue, Army Green, Black, Orange, Dark Green, Light Blue, Rose Red, Navy, Wine Red, Khaki, Pink, White, Beige. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
